        <active>true</active>
        <article><![CDATA[<p>OPTIONALLY, if you have trouble establishing direct connections with endpoints, you may want to disable the &#34;<em>glide.http.outbound.max_timeout.enabled</em>&#34; System Property by setting it to false. This will apply to <em>all</em> HTTP transactions, and will remove the maximum HTTP timeout limit, which otherwise has a maximum value of 30 seconds. <br />If the <em>glide.http.outbound.max_timeout.enabled</em> System Property does not exist, you may need to create it. </p>
<p>You only need to do this if you&#39;re having trouble establishing direct connections with endpoints from ServiceNow. You may skip this step otherwise. </p>]]></article>
